metadata.name: Build an Ape
metadata.description:
"This artwork may or may not be notable." - Jack Butcher

Build an Ape - a project to help the BAYC community reclaim their boredom! For those who may not be familiar, The Tailor strives to make derivative art accessible for non artists in the Web3 community. I want to welcome you to Build an Ape a derivative toolkit that allows holders to build an ape from the ground up choosing the traits you want.

Owning a Build an Ape not only unlocks a realm of creativity, it also provides holders with burnable tokens to make use of on the blockchain. We guarantee that no matter your level of design skills, customization is user friendly and anyone can do it!

Come join our on-chain social experiment! Apes together strong!
